FORM convert_mrec_gas_units  CHANGING p_zpra_t_mrec_prd TYPE zpra_t_mrec_prd.
 DATA : lv_qty TYPE char50 .
* First Convert to MCM

 CASE p_zpra_t_mrec_prd-prod_vl_uom1 .
