*      -->P_GJAHR  text
*      <--P_GJAHR_DAYS  text
*----------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM get_gjahr_days  USING    p_gjahr
                     CHANGING p_gjahr_days.

CALL FUNCTION 'FIRST_AND_LAST_DAY_IN_YEAR_GET'
  EXPORTING
    i_gjahr              = p_gjahr
    i_periv              = gv_periv
 IMPORTING
   e_first_day          = gv_start_date
   e_last_day           = gv_end_date
 EXCEPTIONS
